E. C. GOOLSBY v. WALTER R. CLARK, as Sheriff of Broward County, Florida, and L. T. CLAIBORNE. 17 So. (2nd) 124

January Term, 1944

February 25, 1944 Division A *203John W. Whelan,’for appellant. E. B. Griffis and Rogers, Morris & Griffis, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The record and briefs having been duly considered and no error appearing, the decree is affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J„ TERRELL, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
